import React, { useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import styles from "./LoanForm.module.css"; const LoanForm = () => { const [data, setData] = useState({ ownHouse: "", maritalStatus: "", dependents: "", loanPurpose: "", income: "", creditScore: "", employmentDuration: "", previousHikeDate: "", nextHikeDate: "", existingLoans: "", }); const [result, setResult] = useState(null); const handleChange = (e) => { setData({ ...data, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); axios .post("http://localhost:5000/predict", data) .then((response) => { setResult(response.data); }) .catch((error) => { console.error("Error submitting form", error); }); }; return (

Loan Eligibility Form

{result && (

Prediction Result:

Eligibility: {result.Eligibility ? "Eligible" : "Not Eligible"}

Requested Loan Amount: {result.Requested_Loan_Amount}

Preferred Repayment Period: {result.Preferred_Repayment_Period}

EMI: {result.EMI}

Risk Score: {result.Risk_Score}

)}
); }; export default LoanForm;
